{"tid":701612,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"台灣節目抄足水曜日のダウンタウン片頭","createTime":"2018-06-14T09:18:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-09T15:04:06.000Z","uid":55981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"0a2bf9270d51a3247503e87d7af868b7ca741f29","tid":701612,"uid":55981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-14T09:18:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vQ1z19u4YCQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DvQ1z19u4YCQ&d=3ixQF1WCGVff7VOvrrywgfiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=47275641\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vQ1z19u4YCQ</a><br />\n<br />\n來自星星的事<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cf1obMLwleY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dcf1obMLwleY&d=3ixQF1WCGVff7VOvrrywgfiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=652f1e5b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cf1obMLwleY</a><br />\n<br />\n台灣節目這下紅到日本啦！<br />\n<br />\n日本知名綜藝節目「水曜日のダウンタウン」製作人藤井健太郎日前在推特上指出「台灣節目抄襲&quot;水曜日のダウンタウン&quot;的片頭」引發網友熱烈討論。<br />\n<br />\n藤井健太郎在推特上發文「聽說&quot;水曜日のダウンタウン&quot;的片頭被台灣節目抄走了，看過之後，比我想像中的還像10倍，真有趣」，藤井健太郎還附上這個台灣節目的YouTube，原來是庹宗康所主持的談話性節目《來自星星的事》。<br />\n<br />\n藤井健太郎發文後，這篇《來自星星的事》影片底下，瞬間引來許多日本網友留言，許多日本網友留言表示「這節目是水曜日？」「水曜日？」「這有侵害到著作權嗎？」「這沒有違法嗎？」，意外引發熱議。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180614/640_0130a1dc8629fd70229a9750c60b09c6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180614%2F640_0130a1dc8629fd70229a9750c60b09c6.jpg&h=ae6480ba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180614/640_2c6a8648a9b0839ab2f1892286fa7325.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180614%2F640_2c6a8648a9b0839ab2f1892286fa7325.jpg&h=1d496f09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180614/640_1abb2c46b41525de99bfcb0a7523e7a3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180614%2F640_1abb2c46b41525de99bfcb0a7523e7a3.jpg&h=91467212&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20180614/640_b7c178075bf4f15f095512838ea918c9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20180614%2F640_b7c178075bf4f15f095512838ea918c9.jpg&h=593340f5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"aedf7710ed2d096b4ffa30c57d2cf086035a63ca","tid":701612,"uid":163554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-09T15:04:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}